active_skill.name: Falling Bangboo Asteroid Strike!
active_skill.description:
Charges up and rises into the air, entering Airborne state. While in the Airborne state, Brawlerboo will dive attack enemies when they're hit by a heavy attack from an Agent, dealing Fire DMG.

DMG Multiplier:
840%/896%/952%/1008%/1064%

Daze Multiplier:
492%/524.8%/557.6%/590.4%/623.2%

Cooldown 28s

additional_ability.name: Opening Jab
additional_ability.description:
When another character in your squad is an Attack or Anomaly character:

Brawlerboo enters the Airborne state ahead of time when the battle starts. The first dive attack's DMG is increased by 120%/150%/180%/210%/240%.

chain_attack.name: Scorching Wind Strike
chain_attack.description:
Jump up and strike continuously at enemies in a large area ahead, dealing Fire DMG.

DMG Multiplier:
1269%/1353.6%/1438.2%/1522.8%/1607.3%

Daze Multiplier:
181.5%/193.6%/205.7%/217.8%/229.9%
